wiki_sections.History:
thumb|left|Hagoromo and Hamura sealing the Ten-Tails.
Hagoromo and Hamura Ōtsutsuki used this technique on the Ten-Tails, sealing its body within the newly-created moon. Centuries later, the spirit of Hagoromo passed on the seals required to activate this technique to Naruto Uzumaki and Sasuke Uchiha, who went on to perform the same feat, resealing Kaguya Ōtsutsuki — alongside Black Zetsu — inside of a new moon contained within her core dimension.
{{-L}}

